1
00:00:06,980 --> 00:00:09,289
[Summon Military Commissioner Chen Ying to Chang'an with his troops.]

2
00:00:09,289 --> 00:00:11,579
Although Father left some evidence,

3
00:00:11,579 --> 00:00:14,129
it's still not easy to redress an old case.

4
00:00:14,129 --> 00:00:16,509
Qin Luan and his eunuchs buy and sell information in Rugui House

5
00:00:16,509 --> 00:00:18,271
and monitor the court.
[The imperial stateliness is gone]

6
00:00:18,271 --> 00:00:21,320
Chang'an is disturbed by Duke Chang.

7
00:00:21,320 --> 00:00:23,850
Qianzhou is even more perilous.

8
00:00:27,150 --> 00:00:28,650
Take her!

9
00:00:29,950 --> 00:00:31,809
I don't want to implicate Commandery Prince An.

10
00:00:31,810 --> 00:00:35,610
- Minister Xue.
- I can only do my duty as a coroner.

11
00:00:41,300 --> 00:00:42,999
Tell me the truth.

12
00:00:43,000 --> 00:00:46,520
When did you fall in love with Chu Chu?

13
00:00:47,930 --> 00:00:49,430
Sir…

14
00:00:50,080 --> 00:00:52,520
It's true that I haven't married.

15
00:00:52,520 --> 00:00:55,939
But at my age, do you think I can't figure out

16
00:00:55,939 --> 00:00:57,999
what is going on between you two?

17
00:00:58,000 --> 00:01:00,780
The way you protected Chu Chu.

18
00:01:01,300 --> 00:01:04,660
Jinyu, you lost your mind.

19
00:01:05,520 --> 00:01:08,929
I dare not justify myself in front of you, sir.

20
00:01:08,930 --> 00:01:14,010
In addition to the complicated situation, I did have a selfish motive

21
00:01:14,010 --> 00:01:16,009
when I protected her today.

22
00:01:16,010 --> 00:01:19,649
I know I was being unfair, but it's my own wishful thinking.

23
00:01:19,650 --> 00:01:23,330
If you want to scold me, I won't have any complaints.

24
00:01:23,930 --> 00:01:26,720
Well, well. I don't know what you are thinking.

25
00:01:26,720 --> 00:01:30,009
There are so many noble girls in Chang'an.

26
00:01:30,010 --> 00:01:32,899
Why do you have to fall for a coroner?

27
00:01:32,899 --> 00:01:35,189
If Princess Xiping learns of it, if the emperor learns of it,

28
00:01:35,190 --> 00:01:36,779
do you think a scolding is all you are going to get?

29
00:01:36,780 --> 00:01:38,209
She's not only a coroner.

30
00:01:38,210 --> 00:01:39,889
I know what you want to say.

31
00:01:39,890 --> 00:01:42,109
Her biological parents were also officials.

32
00:01:42,109 --> 00:01:46,929
But she was raised and educated by a family of coroners.

33
00:01:46,930 --> 00:01:50,859
She even went to Chang'an to take the Coroner Qualification Test in the Three Judicial Offices.

34
00:01:50,859 --> 00:01:54,059
Her being a survivor of the rebellious party has been widely talked about in court.

35
00:01:54,059 --> 00:01:56,039
Now everyone in Chang'an knows it.

36
00:01:56,039 --> 00:02:00,379
You should know these taints of her are difficult to clean.

37
00:02:00,380 --> 00:02:03,279
If you are going to make such a mistake,

38
00:02:03,280 --> 00:02:05,860
I will have no choice but to take her away.

39
00:02:08,170 --> 00:02:10,579
I don't mean to offend you.

40
00:02:10,580 --> 00:02:13,129
- But right now, I won't leave her to anyone.
- You...

41
00:02:13,129 --> 00:02:18,169
The so-called taints are what made her who she is today.

42
00:02:18,170 --> 00:02:20,249
I cherish them and value them.

43
00:02:20,250 --> 00:02:22,430
I don't see them as taints.

44
00:02:22,430 --> 00:02:25,089
Besides, you were also born in poverty.

45
00:02:25,090 --> 00:02:26,599
Your achievements are attributed to your own efforts.

46
00:02:26,599 --> 00:02:28,599
I've been listening to your teachings since childhood.

47
00:02:28,599 --> 00:02:30,729
I know that one's fate is not decided by God.

48
00:02:30,730 --> 00:02:32,319
I never judge people by their family.

49
00:02:32,319 --> 00:02:35,499
What you said today contradicts what you taught me before.

50
00:02:35,500 --> 00:02:39,330
I'm confused. Please enlighten me.

51
00:02:39,780 --> 00:02:43,409
Forget it. You've gotten more articulate now.

52
00:02:45,920 --> 00:02:48,140
Thank you for giving me a chance.

53
